title: "Escepcional De La Espanola"
provenance: Collection of Carol B. Brener and Stephen W. Brener
description: In the form of a hand-rolled cigar, with red and white enamelled label inscribed "Escepcional De La Espanola," reverse of label features coat of arms. Last quarter of cigar, where simulated rolled tobacco is visible, flips open as box lid, hinged on reverse. Rolled tobacco at tip likley intended as striker.
